="500"/></a:spcBef><a:buFont typeface="Arial" panose="020B0604020202020204" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/><a:defRPr sz="1800" kern="1200"><a:solidFill><a:schemeClr val="tx1"/></a:solidFill><a:latin typeface="+mn-lt"/><a:ea typeface="+mn-ea"/><a:cs typeface="+mn-cs"/></a:defRPr></a:lvl9pPr></a:lstStyle><a:p><a:pPr fontAlgn="base"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1400" b="0" i="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="000000"/></a:solidFill><a:effectLst/></a:rPr><a:t> </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1600"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="000000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>When photographing various locations and landscapes, we capture the synergy between different perspectives and focal points. </a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr fontAlgn="base"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1600"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="000000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>Looking at the world through different "lenses" and multiple angles illustrates how Interwell looks at the future of energy, transcending energy types and finding new solutions.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr fontAlgn="base"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1600"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="000000"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>We combine organic materials and forms with man-made architecture and geometric shapes. We look at things up close from a micro-focus to zooming out and showing the macro view – visualizing how at Interwell we deliver on every little detail, without ever losing sight of the big picture or the surroundings we work in.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr algn="l" rtl="0" fontAlgn="base"/><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" sz="1400" b="0" i="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="000000"/></a:solidFill><a:effectLst/></a:endParaRPr></a:p><a:p><a:pPr algn="l" rtl="0" fontAlgn="base"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1400" b="0" i="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="000000"/></a:solidFill><a:effectLst/></a:rPr><a:t>  </a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-GB"/></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="en-GB"/></a:p><a:p><a:endParaRPr lang="